room_title: Escape room "The Malt Shop" by Riddle Me Roanoke in Roanoke
room_description: Your malt shop has proven to be the most popular in Roanoke! Unfortunately, a new competitor recently stole your recipes and has started capitalizing on them.  You need to get the recipes back before your business suffers any further loss.  Your only option is to break in during the night and take back what is rightfully yours. Can you get in and out without getting caught?
